title: Butterfly (disambiguation)
content:
Butterfly may refer to:

  • Butterfly, insects found throughout Gielinor
  • Butterfly (Hunter), butterflies caught using the Hunter skill
    • Ruby harvest, a level 15 Hunter creature
    • Sapphire glacialis, a level 25 Hunter creature
    • Snowy knight, a level 35 Hunter creature
    • Black warlock, a level 45 Hunter creature
  • Butterfly net, used to catch butterflies and implings
    • Magic butterfly net, an upgraded version of the butterfly net
  • Butterfly (troll), a troll in Weiss
  • Butterfly jar, used to catch butterflies
    • Ruby harvest (item), an item that can temporarily boost another player's Attack
    • Sapphire glacialis (item), an item that can temporarily boost another player's Defence
    • Snowy knight (item), an item that can heal another player's Hitpoints
    • Black warlock (item), an item that can boost another player's Strength
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
